com.google.gxp.compiler.alerts
Class SourcePosition

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gxp.compiler.alerts.SourcePosition
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public final class SourcePosition
extends Object
implements Serializable

Value object for representing a position in a source file. The line and column postions can be left out. This is to support alerts that don't have a specific location in a file.
